728,"enterprise_value":479054016.0,"enterprise_to_ebitda":14.432,"enterprise_to_revenue":1.377,"earnings_growth":-0.607,"shares_outstanding":2534952.0,"float_shares":568764.0,"held_pct_insiders":0.84378,"held_pct_institutions":0.022090001,"beta":-0.403,"fifty_two_week_high":216.0,"fifty_two_week_low":145.0,"fifty_day_average":164.46,"two_hundred_day_avg":187.65726,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":276.8,"all_time_low":84.6,"long_business_summary":"Rex Sealing and Packing Industries Limited manufactures and sells sealing, packing, and insulation products in India and internationally. The company offers compressed non asbestos jointing sheets, such as steam, high pressure steam, oil, special oil, and acid jointing sheets; and gland packing products comprising PTFE fiber, synthetic PTFE fiber, PTFE graphite, pure aramid fiber, pure graphite, GFO, aramid + GFO fiber, PTFE aramid, PTFE graphite gland, pure carbon with graphite, ultra-pure graphite fiber, and carbonaceous aramid fiber packing products. It also provides fabric expansion joints, insulation jackets, ceramic fiber products, fire resistant sleeves and mattes, tadpole gaskets, graphite sheets and rings, and vermiculite coated cloth; ropes and high temperature resistant textiles; and silica and silicone products, such as silica tape with adhesive, silica cloth, high temperature silica products, silica fabrics, and insulating silica fabrics. The company serves the petrochemical, power, cement, steel, chemical, pharmaceutical, gas, and process industries. It also exports its products to various industries in the United Kingdom, the United States, Europe, Australia, Africa, and the Middle East. Rex Sealing and Packing Industries Limited was founded in 1963 and is based in Raigad, India."}}